"1 teaspoon olive oil","  Cooking spray","3 cups thinly sliced mushrooms","1 cup chopped onion","1 cup chopped red bell pepper","3 cups chopped fresh spinach","1 tablespoon chopped fresh oregano","1/4 teaspoon freshly ground black pepper","1  (16-ounce) carton 2% low-fat cottage cheese","4 cups hot cooked penne (about 8 ounces uncooked tube-shaped pasta)","2 cups shredded roasted skinless, boneless chicken breast","1 cup (4 ounces) shredded reduced-fat sharp cheddar cheese, divided","1/2 cup (2 ounces) grated fresh Parmesan cheese, divided","1/2 cup 2% reduced-fat milk","1  (10 3/4-ounce) can condensed reduced-fat, reduced-sodium cream of chicken soup, undiluted"